<i>into the World Trade Center.</i>

00:42.409 --> 00:43.967
<i>...thousands of people running-</i>

00:44.044 --> 00:46.342
We must, and we will...

00:46.413 --> 00:47.971
remain vigilant at home and abroad.

00:53.887 --> 00:55.514
<i>What the fuck are you doing?</i>

00:57.824 --> 01:00.019
<i>Fuckl I missed something once before.</i>

01:00.093 --> 01:03.119
<i>I won't- I can't let that happen again.</i>

01:05.364 --> 01:07.959
<i>It was 10 years ago.</i>
<i>Everyone missed something that day.</i>

01:08.034 --> 01:10.696
<i>Yeah, everyone is not me.</i>

01:10.770 --> 01:12.032
<i>Once you've gotten to this position.</i>

01:19.546 --> 01:21.343
<i>Previously on</i> Homeland.

01:21.414 --> 01:24.975
You're telling me the fucking C.I.A.
Thinks I'm working for Al-Qaeda?

01:25.051 --> 01:27.042
<i>I think you're working for Al-Qaeda.</i>

01:27.120 --> 01:30.021
<i>- Ask me anything.</i>
<i>- What goes on in your garage?</i>

01:30.090 --> 01:32.991
Why do you go there so late at night,
so early in the morning?

01:33.059 --> 01:34.117
To pray.

01:34.194 --> 01:35.684
You're a Muslim?

01:35.762 --> 01:38.230
Why did they kill Walker and not you?

01:38.298 --> 01:40.129
I killed him.

01:40.200 --> 01:42.327
- <i>Who told you to kill him?</i>
- <i>Abu Nazir.</i>

01:42.402 --> 01:44.529
- <i>So you did meet him.</i>
- <i>Yes.</i>

01:44.604 --> 01:46.970
- If you want to arrest me,
you can come to my house.
- No. Brody!

01:47.040 --> 01:48.735
We were wrong about Brody.

01:48.808 --> 01:51.242
<i>A P.O.W.</i> was <i>turned. It wasn't him.</i>

01:51.311 --> 01:53.472
Aileen just I.D.'d Tom Walker.

01:53.546 --> 01:56.879
- Tom Walker died.
- No. He's the terrorist.

01:58.251 --> 02:00.344
Tom was dead. That's what they told me.

02:00.420 --> 02:03.218
What we need to do is find him
before anything happens.

02:03.289 --> 02:05.348
Oh, baby, I've done a horrible thing.

02:05.425 --> 02:08.656
- No, Helen, no. Don't!
- They're tracing this call!
You got to get out of there!

02:11.331 --> 02:12.525
Gun!

02:14.334 --> 02:17.394
The tac team followed Walker here.
Two casualties.

02:17.470 --> 02:19.597
Local Muslims here for morning prayer.

02:19.672 --> 02:22.732
<i>... Congressman Richard</i>
<i>Johnson caught in a sexting scandal...</i>

02:22.809 --> 02:27.678
<i>sending nude and seminude</i>
<i>pictures of himself to a number</i>
<i>of congressional interns.</i>

02:27.747 --> 02:32.241
He'll be gone in two days.
I have an idea who might replace him.

02:32.318 --> 02:35.719
- Are you crazy?
- You people told me Walker was dead.

02:35.788 --> 02:37.551
I don't-

02:37.624 --> 02:39.285
My friend!

02:39.359 --> 02:41.884
You told me I killed him.

02:41.961 --> 02:44.521
- You made me believe!
- I don't know!

02:44.597 --> 02:47.532
Really! You have to talk to Abu Nazir!

02:49.469 --> 02:53.530
