03:57.770 --> 03:59.795
What's Dad say?

03:59.872 --> 04:02.466
So far, not a whole lot.

04:02.542 --> 04:06.103
- Well, have you even asked him?
- Yes, Dana, of course I've asked him.

04:06.179 --> 04:10.275
He can't believe it.
He says there's gotta be some mistake.

04:10.350 --> 04:12.614
It's not the first time
the F.B.I. Have gotten it wrong.

04:12.685 --> 04:14.448
Yeah, but what if they're right?

04:14.520 --> 04:18.616
Two marines are captured,
and one comes back a terrorist?

04:20.360 --> 04:22.328
Dad must be going out of his mind.

04:22.395 --> 04:25.125
Did you find everything
you were looking for today, sir?

04:25.198 --> 04:27.325
- Yes. Thank you.
- You're welcome.

04:29.535 --> 04:31.730
- Just one thing.
- Yeah.

04:31.804 --> 04:34.830
- What does that say?
- Vitamin Water.

04:34.907 --> 04:37.740
- What is that?
