04:37.810 --> 04:40.802
Would you like me to get
someone to find it for you?

04:41.381 --> 04:43.076
What flavor?

04:43.149 --> 04:45.014
I don't know. What you got?

04:45.084 --> 04:46.517
Um-

04:46.586 --> 04:48.850
Hey. You're that marine
war hero guy, right?

06:02.729 --> 06:05.197
We have nothing to do
but pray for our brothers...

06:05.264 --> 06:07.494
that they will go into heaven for God.

06:07.567 --> 06:10.593
The F.B.I. Said
that they were fired at first-

06:10.670 --> 06:12.103
which is a lie.

06:12.171 --> 06:14.639
The truth is they shot and killed...

06:14.707 --> 06:17.437
two innocent people in a house of worship,
without provocation.

06:17.510 --> 06:19.034
Hey.

06:19.112 --> 06:21.512
What about
the man they were chasing- Tom Walker?

06:21.581 --> 06:23.742
- What do you know about him?
- All any of us know...

06:23.816 --> 06:25.716
is that a stranger
ran through our mosque...

06:25.785 --> 06:29.050
being chased by F.B.I. Agents while we
were gathering for morning prayers.

06:29.122 --> 06:31.716
Have you been told the
names of the agents who fired the shots?

06:31.791 --> 06:33.588
No, we're still awaiting
a full investigation.

06:33.659 --> 06:36.253
We don't know anything yet.

06:36.329 --> 06:38.991
No, sir. We do not condone hate.

06:39.065 --> 06:40.999
Or violence.

06:42.368 --> 06:44.336
Ms. Mathison.

06:44.404 --> 06:46.372
Special Agent Hall.

06:46.439 --> 06:49.806
I asked to meet the SWAT team commander,
the man who was on the ground for this.

06:49.876 --> 06:52.310
And you got me. His boss.

06:52.378 --> 06:56.212
- How can I help?
- Would you mind taking
your shoes off, please?

07:01.187 --> 07:03.155
What are we doing here exactly?

07:03.222 --> 07:05.122
Everything we can to catch Walker.

07:05.191 --> 07:08.183
You're aware there's an F.B.I.
Manhunt up and running.

07:08.261 --> 07:11.424
All 56 field offices, canceled leave-

07:11.497 --> 07:13.692
The reason why I asked to meet
the actual SWAT commander...

07:13.766 --> 07:16.428
is because I need him to walk me
through exactly what happened here.

07:16.502 --> 07:18.333
Which he already did with me.

07:18.404 --> 07:22.898
So, Walker comes in from the alley,
through this door here.

07:22.975 --> 07:26.877
And we already know he was armed,
because he stole a gun from one of your men.

07:26.946 --> 07:28.538
And?

07:28.614 --> 07:30.411
Did Walker open fire first?

07:31.117 --> 07:32.641
Yes.

07:32.718 --> 07:35.710
Yet the imam is standing
out there telling the world that's a lie.

07:35.788 --> 07:38.848
The imam? That's his word against mine.

07:38.925 --> 07:41.689
He also says that neither
he nor any of his flock know Walker.

07:41.761 --> 07:43.422
Which is not true.

07:43.496 --> 07:45.589
Do you want to know why?

07:45.665 --> 07:48.099
- Please.
- Then walk with me.

07:49.735 --> 07:53.831
He hauls ass down these stairs
to a service corridor that goes left...

07:53.906 --> 07:55.737
to a janitor's storage room...

07:55.808 --> 07:59.471
or right, doubling back underneath the
building to a Bilco door on Raum Street...

07:59.545 --> 08:01.809
all the way on the east side
of the building.

08:01.881 --> 08:04.349
Son of a bitch goes right.

08:04.417 --> 08:06.510
He knew exactly
where the fuck he was going.

08:06.586 --> 08:08.952
You following me on this so far?

08:09.021 --> 08:11.649
- He knows this mosque.
- Correct.

08:12.892 --> 08:15.588
And probably a lot of people
that come here too.

08:42.355 --> 08:43.720
<i>As-salaam alaikum.</i>

08:43.789 --> 08:46.053
<i>Alaikum salaam.</i>

08:46.125 --> 08:49.754
Imam, let me begin by saying
how deeply sorry I am for your loss.

08:49.829 --> 08:51.626
Losses. Plural.

08:51.697 --> 08:53.961
There were two dead.

09:00.973 --> 09:02.668
Lmam, my name is Carrie Mathison.

09:02.742 --> 09:06.075
Another government official here to
suggest that if we weren't all guilty...

09:06.145 --> 09:08.477
one way or another,
none of this would have happened, right?

09:16.789 --> 09:21.351
I'm also well aware of your
good work in this neighborhood,
beyond just here in the mosque.

09:21.427 --> 09:23.759
Then you should know
how violated we all feel.

09:23.829 --> 09:25.490
I do. Yes.

09:25.565 --> 09:29.968
I have seven eyewitnesses,
including myself, who saw what happened.

09:30.036 --> 09:33.494
Please forgive me,
but my job right now- my only job-

09:33.573 --> 09:36.098
is to catch this man Walker
as soon as possible.

09:36.175 --> 09:38.439
He did not fire
a single shot at the agents.

09:38.511 --> 09:40.775
He was moving too fast,
trying to get away from them.

09:40.846 --> 09:43.644
Either Walker was very lucky to get away
as quickly as he did...

09:43.716 --> 09:46.776
or he knew this mosque
well enough to use it as an escape route.

09:48.521 --> 09:50.546
I have families to comfort.

09:50.623 --> 09:52.591
I have funerals to arrange.

09:52.658 --> 09:55.718
I have a community who believes they will
never get justice for what happened.

09:55.795 --> 09:59.526
If you do know Walker,
or anything about him...

09:59.599 --> 10:01.999
or anyone who might...

10:02.068 --> 10:05.629
whatever you tell us, no matter how small,
would be in total confidence.

10:06.906 --> 10:09.136
And yet you offer me nothing in return.

10:10.276 --> 10:12.210
What do you mean by that?

10:12.278 --> 10:14.246
Specifically. Just so I'm clear.

10:14.313 --> 10:18.477
Two families will get no justice, unless
the F.B.I. Tells the truth...

10:18.551 --> 10:22.180
about how they killed two innocent people
who were doing nothing but pray.

10:23.723 --> 10:25.714
In other words, you <i>do</i> know something.

10:29.795 --> 10:31.456
Good-bye, Ms. Mathison.

10:31.530 --> 10:33.395
Mr. Galvez.

10:35.835 --> 10:37.803
He knows Walker. You saw that, right?

10:37.870 --> 10:40.134
- I'm not crazy?
- You're not crazy.

10:40.206 --> 10:43.437
I don't give a shit what it takes-
that imam is gonna talk to me.

10:43.509 --> 10:45.704
What it takes?
He wants a full F.B.I. Mea culpa.

10:45.778 --> 10:47.803
Good luck with that.

10:50.016 --> 10:53.247
It's not medicine. It's a drink.

10:53.319 --> 10:57.346
Dana likes the "Revive" flavor,
and Chris likes the "Energy" one.

10:57.423 --> 10:59.482
And Dana's been asking a lot
about Tom Walker.

10:59.558 --> 11:01.856
It's all over the Internet,
and I don't really have any answers...

11:01.927 --> 11:03.952
so if you can come home
as soon as you can-

11:04.030 --> 11:08.524
Oh, I told Chris that I would take him to a
movie if he got all his homework done today.

11:08.601 --> 11:14.233
He specifically asked if you would
come too, so just call me back. Okay?

12:53.773 --> 12:56.367
This is your new home now.

13:09.822 --> 13:11.653
Come.

15:09.608 --> 15:11.633
This is Issa, my son.

15:22.454 --> 15:23.978
<i>As-salaam alaikum.</i>

15:25.824 --> 15:29.555
Issa.

15:32.898 --> 15:34.490
Issa.

15:35.935 --> 15:37.994
<i>Wa alaikum assalam.</i>

15:39.338 --> 15:42.899
I want him to learn English- fluently.

15:42.975 --> 15:46.809
You will live here with him
as long as it takes.

16:09.835 --> 16:12.030
I have no clue how to do this.

16:13.505 --> 16:15.496
I'm not a teacher.

16:43.035 --> 16:45.026
- We have a problem.
- Hey.

16:45.104 --> 16:48.562
What, are you stalking me now?
How'd you find me here?

16:49.808 --> 16:52.436
- They spent years training me.
- Ah.

16:52.511 --> 16:56.242
- So, what's the problem?
- The imam.

16:56.315 --> 16:59.079
- He'll calm down in a day or two.
- I don't have a day or two.

16:59.151 --> 17:01.585
- He says your men fired first.
- I know what he's saying.

17:01.653 --> 17:03.678
He has seven eyewitnesses,
including himself...

17:03.756 --> 17:06.247
saying Walker didn't shoot
or even raise a weapon at them.

17:07.826 --> 17:08.815
And?

17:10.628 --> 17:13.119
I believe he's withholding
information about Walker.

17:13.198 --> 17:15.462
Well, you people have
rubber hoses, don't you?

17:15.534 --> 17:17.968
He's a good man caught in a bad situation.

17:18.037 --> 17:21.973
He runs a mosque that a terrorist suspect
used as an escape route.

17:22.040 --> 17:24.339
He wants justice for the men
who were killed...

17:24.410 --> 17:26.742
for which I think he'll tell me
what he knows about Walker.

17:27.980 --> 17:30.210
Justice?

17:30.282 --> 17:32.011
What does that mean?

17:32.084 --> 17:36.180
Well, for one thing,
it means compensation for the families.

17:36.255 --> 17:41.056
Look, if one of your men made a mistake,
you need to come clean.

17:41.126 --> 17:44.459
Let me ask you something.
Have you ever been in a firefight?

17:44.530 --> 17:46.020
Yes.

17:48.967 --> 17:51.026
Okay.

17:52.204 --> 17:54.502
So, my men follow
an armed terrorist suspect...

17:54.573 --> 17:56.632
based off intel provided by you people...

17:56.708 --> 18:00.269
at zero dark 30 into a fucking building
that they don't even know is a mosque.

18:00.345 --> 18:03.371
In seconds, a member of the team
thinks he has a clear shot...

18:03.449 --> 18:05.917
at bringing down a terrorist,
and he takes it.

18:05.984 --> 18:09.385
Accidentally,
he drops two civilians in the cross fire.

18:09.455 --> 18:11.218
Shit happens.

18:12.291 --> 18:14.816
But if you think that I or the Bureau...

18:14.893 --> 18:18.624
are gonna let the C.I.A. Come in
and throw any of my guys under the bus...

18:19.498 --> 18:21.762
you're fucking high.

18:41.053 --> 18:45.217
Hey. Hey, Issa.
Come closer. Don't be afraid.

18:45.290 --> 18:47.019
Come on.

18:47.092 --> 18:49.151
Wanna play?

18:53.599 --> 18:56.090
Hey. Hey, you know how to do this?

19:00.072 --> 19:02.472
Can you do this? Yeah?

19:03.642 --> 19:06.076
You want to learn?

19:08.347 --> 19:10.315
Yeah?

19:11.683 --> 19:13.446
Look. Soccer ball.

19:13.519 --> 19:15.350
It's a soccer ball.

19:15.420 --> 19:18.218
Soccer.
Can you say that? Soccer.

19:18.290 --> 19:19.382
Socce-

19:20.859 --> 19:21.883
Hey.

19:23.729 --> 19:26.493
Hey. Hey, Issa.

19:27.199 --> 19:28.689
Hey, wait.

19:30.602 --> 19:35.733
<i>Accidentally, he drops two</i>
<i>civilians in the cross fire. Shit happens.</i>

19:35.807 --> 19:38.799
<i>But if you think that I or the Bureau...</i>

19:38.877 --> 19:42.904
<i>are gonna let the C.I.A. Come in</i>
<i>and throw any of my guys under the bus...</i>

19:42.981 --> 19:45.381
<i>you're fucking high.</i>

19:46.919 --> 19:51.117
You're really fucking something, Carrie.
I gotta hand it to you.

19:51.190 --> 19:54.387
There is no bridge you won't burn,
no earth you won't scorch.

19:54.459 --> 19:56.393
When it comes to catching Walker...

19:56.461 --> 19:58.793
or any terrorist suspect for that matter,
damn straight.

19:58.864 --> 20:00.832
You recorded a senior F.B.I. Agent...

20:00.899 --> 20:03.493
who thought he was talking off the record
to someone on the same side...

20:03.569 --> 20:06.367
so you could leverage
the F.B.I. Into admitting a mistake.

20:06.438 --> 20:08.770
Are you really prepared
to sacrifice the very agency that...

20:08.840 --> 20:11.775
with all their manpower,
is the best chance we have to get Walker?

20:11.843 --> 20:14.641
They accidentally
shot and killed two people.

20:14.713 --> 20:17.614
Now, I get that it's not easy,
or even ideal...

20:17.683 --> 20:20.811
but we need to convince them to just
make a statement taking responsibility.

20:20.886 --> 20:22.649
For what?

20:22.721 --> 20:26.782
The hope that this imam will give you
information that you don't even know he has?

20:26.858 --> 20:29.759
No disrespect, David, but I think
I've been in the field long enough...

20:29.828 --> 20:32.092
to know a source when I see one.

20:36.468 --> 20:39.028
You will not- I repeat- not...

20:39.104 --> 20:42.938
do anything to sabotage
the F.B.I. Manhunt for Walker.

20:43.008 --> 20:44.805
That is a direct order.

21:07.232 --> 21:09.223
What happened here?

21:11.803 --> 21:14.636
I was showing him a trick with the ball...

21:14.706 --> 21:16.901
and I, uh- I knocked over some glasses.

22:06.391 --> 22:08.450
What the hell...

22:08.527 --> 22:11.428
- are you doing, Carrie?
- What? Nothing.

22:13.598 --> 22:15.793
The last I checked, this was my office.

22:15.867 --> 22:20.736
Just- I needed
somewhere private to calm down.

22:20.806 --> 22:22.467
Somewhere private?

22:22.541 --> 22:24.702
Okay, so I was hoping you'd be here.
Where have you been?

22:25.877 --> 22:29.278
I just heard about the imam and the F.B.I.

22:29.348 --> 22:31.077
Estes is right.

22:31.149 --> 22:35.381
That imam knows Walker.
I fucking know it, 100%.

22:35.454 --> 22:38.651
- You think the imam's bad?
- No. No. That's the problem.

22:38.724 --> 22:43.024
He's practically a saint. I've got nothing
on him. I've got zero leverage.

22:43.095 --> 22:46.360
- You're 100% sure he's not bad?
- Pretty much.

22:52.304 --> 22:53.999
So?

22:55.540 --> 22:58.065
Maybe you're approaching
the problem the wrong way around.

23:27.773 --> 23:29.536
<i>Allahu Akbar.</i>

23:29.608 --> 23:31.701
<i>Allahu Akbar.</i>

